
   Dibbler - a portable DHCPv6
  -----------------------------
  authors: Tomasz Mrugalski <thomson@klub.com.pl>
           Marek Senderski <msend@o2.pl>
           
   Ports available
  -----------------
  Linux - Tomasz Mrugalski
  WinXP - Marek Senderski
  Win2k - Tomasz Mrugalski/Marek Senderski

  Compilation info
 -----------------------
  just type "make" and have your fingers crossed.
 
  Linux user guide
 ------------------------
  Server start: ./server
  Server start in daemon mode: ./server -d
  Server stop: kill `cat server.pid`

  Server start: ./server
  Server start in daemon mode: ./server -d
  Server stop: kill `cat server.pid`
  
  Additional info
 -----------------
 Newest version is available at http://klub.com.pl/dhcpv6/
 
 